title: ArcGIS Portal Logs
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors recent ArcGIS Portal WARNING and SEVERE log entries.

 The special agent queries Portal logs over a configurable time window. SEVERE
 and WARNING entries are counted separately. Known noisy log messages can be
 suppressed with ignore regexes or ignored log codes in the special agent rule.
 Ignored entries are counted separately and shown in the service summary.

 Recent SEVERE entries are included in the service details for triage.
item:
 This check has no item.
discovery:
 One service is discovered when Portal log data is present.
perfdata:
 The check emits Portal SEVERE and WARNING log counts as metrics.
